---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/page-layout.astro";
---

<PageLayout>
		<div class="hidden mx-auto w-3/4 md:grid grid-cols-2 justify-center content-center gap-5 py-5">
			<div class="self-center grid gap-6">
				<div class="grid gap-2">
					<h1 class="self-center text-4xl font-semibold text-brandBrown">Medieval Reception of the Roman Conquest of Jerusalem </h1>
					<h2 class="self-center text-2xl italic text-brandCaramel">The Roman conquest of Jerusalem in 70 AD: Reception, use, and interpretation in the Middle Ages (c.600-c.1200)</h2>
				</div>
				<p class="text-brandBrown">The project explores the medieval reception and interpretation of the Roman conquest of Jerusalem in 70 AD, examining its presence in chronicles, anti-Jewish treatises, sermon collections, and biblical commentaries.</p>
			</div>
			<figure class="grid gap-2">
				<img class="object-contain w-full" src="./title-image.png" alt="(Venice) La distruzione del tempio di Gerusalemme -Francesco Hayez" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
				<figcaption class="font-light text-xs">La distruzione del tempio di Gerusalemme by Francesco Hayez (Gallerie Accademia Venice; photograph by Didier Descouens - <a class="underline decoration-dotted" href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=132796743">Public Domain</a></figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>
		<div class="md:hidden min-h-full grid content-start mx-auto gap-3 p-5">
			<a href="about.html">
				<article class="grid items-start justify-items-center gap-3 rounded-md border-2 border-brandRed">
					<img class="object-cover h-52" src="./title-image.png" alt="(Venice) La distruzione del tempio di Gerusalemme -Francesco Hayez" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">About the project</h2>
				</article>
			</a>
			<a href="database.html">
				<article class="grid items-start justify-items-center gap-3 rounded-md border-2 border-brandRed">
					<img class="object-cover h-52" src="./database.svg" alt="" loading="lazy">
					<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Search the database</h2>
				</article>
			</a>
		</div>
</PageLayout>